<cb:div>
<pb n="0090a" xml:id="I01.0036.0090a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0090a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 36</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0090a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>安村道俗一百餘人修塔記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0090a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0090a0101">夫脩心始行。必資願表。表願功能。道由生養。生養之功。謂之塔像。故八塔顯自碧林。
<lb ed="I" n="0090a02" type="honorific"/>影髮著之香樹。是使見形立善。<note n="0090001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30611"/>＝範【史】</note><note n="0090001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30611"/>【佛拓】，範【史】</note><app n="0090001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">範</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30611"/></rdg></app>像流今。若非曠積<note n="0090002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30612"/>＝深【史】</note><note n="0090002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30612"/>【佛拓】，深【史】</note><app n="0090002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">深</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30612"/></rdg></app>因。慈悲宿造。則必弱<note n="0090003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB07656"/>＝喪【史】</note><note n="0090003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB07656"/>【佛拓】，喪【史】</note><app n="0090003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB07656"/></rdg></app>忘歸。
<lb ed="I" n="0090a03" type="honorific"/>長迷誰覺。唯雅見君子能改<note n="0090004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𡵯＝步【史】</note><note n="0090004" resp="ihp" type="mod">𡵯【佛拓】，步【史】</note><app n="0090004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">步</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𡵯</rdg></app>迷方。控平軒於一乘。移心弱<app type="star" corresp="#0090003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB07656"/></rdg></app>。汎神舟於三路。是以
<lb ed="I" n="0090a04" type="honorific"/>獲<note n="0090005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30614"/>＝嘉【史】</note><note n="0090005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30614"/>【佛拓】，嘉【史】</note><app n="0090005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嘉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30614"/></rdg></app>縣東。清流福地。號曰安村。有大檀主。　　　置立尼寺。有故天宮一區。<note n="0090006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30618"/>＝年【史】</note><note n="0090006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30618"/>【佛拓】，年【史】</note><app n="0090006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">年</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30618"/></rdg></app>久事
<lb ed="I" n="0090a05" type="honorific"/>遐。神功頓毀。寶色莊嚴。散靈像於輕塵。陵雲雅<note n="0090007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30615"/>＝製【史】</note><note n="0090007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30615"/>【佛拓】，製【史】</note><app n="0090007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">製</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30615"/></rdg></app>。落真儀於重壤。玉地<app type="star" corresp="#0090002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">深</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30612"/></rdg></app>經。髣髴若
<lb ed="I" n="0090a06" type="honorific"/>存。寶相祇林。神容中斷。乃復道俗一百餘人。發悟自心。輕財重道。捨身命財。共脩故
<lb ed="I" n="0090a07" type="honorific"/>塔。始末十旬。微功乃就。復妙相於靈山。<note n="0090008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30616"/>＝還【史】</note><note n="0090008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30616"/>【佛拓】，還【史】</note><app n="0090008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">還</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30616"/></rdg></app>湛一於雙樹。義感去來。精貫<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">現</unclear>在。邈<note n="0090009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30617"/>＝象【史】</note><note n="0090009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30617"/>【佛拓】，象【史】</note><app n="0090009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">象</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30617"/></rdg></app>護
<lb ed="I" n="0090a08" type="honorific"/>於金經。超名敕於玉牒。釋梵來儀。乘碧霧以通煙。四王效像。曜五花於日月。淨水香
<lb ed="I" n="0090a09" type="honorific"/>雲。若<note n="0090010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𩀌＝離【史】</note><note n="0090010" resp="ihp" type="mod">𩀌【佛拓】，離【史】</note><app n="0090010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">離</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𩀌</rdg></app>復合。異物芬芳。殊方恒在。金剛豈遠。此地長春。十種莊嚴。事同紫岸。因茲業
<lb ed="I" n="0090a10" type="honorific"/>也。一百人等。發斯洪願。願令　皇家。寶運<app type="star" corresp="#0090002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">深</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30612"/></rdg></app>基。道契二儀之堅。玉蒂金根。福同九山
<lb ed="I" n="0090a11" type="honorific"/>之宅。異物諍祥。雲華帝門。奇<g ref="#CB30664"/>競像。風翻上國。破四魔於五雲。拔三鋒於四濘。甘露
<lb ed="I" n="0090a12" type="honorific"/>淨音。導一乘於方方。法水金開。灌千迷於莫〃。三有一歸。同軒佛寶。哀鸞和雅。調八
<lb ed="I" n="0090a13" type="honorific"/>梵於清蓮。冥讚空絃。妙龍舟於幽俗。往聖所以懸苻。來賢所以共一。思報四恩。常脩
<lb ed="I" n="0090a14" type="honorific"/>□度。火劍自消。三途永息。莫不盡化<app type="star" corresp="#0090008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">還</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30616"/></rdg></app>无。妙鄰二智。滅諦夷然。誰非佛者。奉慈氏於
<lb ed="I" n="0090a15" type="honorific"/>初覺。會千佛於淨<app type="star" corresp="#0090006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">年</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30618"/></rdg></app>。正心正見。唯願如是。
<lb ed="I" n="0090a16" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　　唯大魏天平四<app type="star" corresp="#0090006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">年</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30618"/></rdg></app>歲次丁巳七月甲午朔廿五日戊午</p>
</cb:div>
